{"tid":524554,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「非打手」法國喜得佳啲丸幾掂 完勝四海","createTime":"2018-01-09T16:48:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T07:43:50.000Z","uid":129221,"like":1,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"676cd125168a57bd020377d983a35380d092ca76","tid":524554,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T16:48:18.000Z","msg":"今晚打邊爐 老婆漏左買丸個啲 叫我放工去買<br />\n咁撚凍緊係唔去街市買靚丸啦<br />\n諗住求其去百佳買四海算數<br />\n點知四海比人清晒貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能今晚凍多人打邊爐啦<br />\n見到隻乜鳩喜得佳full晒貨 心諗一定伏但都要照買<br />\n唔係今晚一定要訓廳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n返到屋企老婆見到黑晒面 想屌鳩我 我即刻話呢隻好食架 頭先見到個師奶買左好多 佢話好味架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我自己都唔想食啲丸 一淥好就夾左粒牛筋丸比老婆 睇住佢擺入口 我木然等待一會兒老婆大人的一頓臭罵 結果令我感到喜出望外 她竟然說：好食！彈牙又有牛味 好似食緊鮮牛咁<br />\n之後其他腸丸都絕對唔差 以佢既價錢絕對物超所值 cp值之選<br />\n唔好屌我打手 真心有好野益連登仔 因為我打完邊爐即刻落左去掃貨先同大家講 試左唔好食再屌我都未遲 好食記得講返聲多謝就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 黎緊想打邊爐既記得去買牛筋丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果要買四海不如買喜得佳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一齊支持香港好牌子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fddea5f003230ac81bfc3e6b23f3dcc89f385306","tid":524554,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T17:15:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1f8f80c131188d573ee35369cc8e4db81fee5f9","tid":524554,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T00:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6efaebf50b452a9efa9e89eab28c22dadab3e9f","tid":524554,"uid":129221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-10T02:36:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj